@node "Where_No_Man_Has_Gone_Before" "Where No Man Has Gone Before"
                                 
                               Episode #001
                        @{b}@{i}WHERE NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE @{ub}@{ui}
                               @{fg fill}Samuel Peeples@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 09-22-66@{fg text}
                         Director: James Goldstone 

   Catalyzed by an energy field in space, the ESP powers latent in both Gary
 Mitchell and psychologist Elizabeth Dehner evolve into mental powers
 approaching omnipotence. Kirk must consider stopping them, or killing them,
 before there powers allow them to control first the Enterprise, then the
 universe.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Gary Mitchell... Gary Lockwood           Kelso...Paul Carr
 Elizabeth Dehner...Sally Kellerman       Dr. Piper...Pual Fix
 Yeoman Smith...Andrea Dromm              Alden...Lloyd Haynes

 @{" Episode Pic " system "VT TrekGuide:TrekPics/EP001"}
 @{" Episode Pic " system "VT TrekGuide:TrekPics/EP001-2"}
 @{"     SFX     " system "run Trekguide:sound TrekGuide:TrekSFX/EP001"}

