@endnode

@node "The_Enemy_Within" "The Enemy Within"

                                 Episode #004
                              @{b}@{i}THE ENEMY WITHIN @{ub}@{ui}
                              @{fg fill}Richard Matheson@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 10-06-66@{fg text}
                            Director: Leo Penn 

   Due to a transporter malfunction, Kirk is beamed aboard split into two 
 identical Kirks, both dangerously weak physically, and each possessing
 different aspects of Kirk's mind; one mild-mannered and frightened, the
 other animalistic and hostile.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 John Ferrell...Jim Goodwin
 Technicians..Edward Madden, Garland Thompson

 NOTE: This is the first episode in which Spock uses the Vulcan Neck Pinch.

 @{" Episode Pic " system "VT TrekGuide:TrekPics/EP004"}

