@node "The_Man_Trap" "The Man Trap"

                                 Episode #005
                                @{b}@{i}THE MAN TRAP @{ub}@{ui}
                             @{fg fill}George Clay Johnson@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 09-15-66@{fg text}
                          Director: Marc Daniels 

   Dr. McCoy finds an old girlfriend married to an archeologist on a desolate
 Planet, but she turns out to be a fatally dangerous illusion: shes's the last
 of an alien race, able to take human form, surviving only by sucking the
 salt from the bodies of humans. McCoy has to learn she is not real. . .
 or perish as others have.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Nancy Carter...Jeanny Bal               Monster...Francine Pyne
 Prof. Carter...Alfred Ryder             Darnell...Michael Zaslow

 @{" Episode Pic " system "VT TrekGuide:TrekPics/EP005"}

