@node "Balance_of_Terror" "Balance of Terror"

                                 Episode #008
                              @{b}@{i}BALANCE OF TERROR @{ub}@{ui}
                               @{fg fill}Paul Schneider@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 12-13-66@{fg text}
                        Director: Vincent McEveety 

  The dreaded @{"Romulans" link "TG_MSC/ROMULAN_EPISODES" 0} use a powerful new weapon to utterly destroy
 Federation Outpost, and an energy screen that makes their ships
 invisible to the Enterprises sensors. Kirk finds a way to follow
 and attack them, and engages in a battle of wits with the Romulan
 Commander.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Romulan Commander...Mark Lenard             Andrew Stiles...Paul Comi
 Decius...Lawrence Montaigne                 Centurion...John Warburton
 Robert Tomlinson...Stephen Mines            Angela Martine...Barbara Baldavin
 Hanson...Gary Walberg

