@node "Shore_Leave" "Shore Leave"

                                 Episode #017
                                 @{b}@{i}SHORE LEAVE @{ub}@{ui}
                              @{fg fill}Theodore Sturgeon@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 12-29-66@{fg text}
                          Director: Robert Sparr

  Kirk gives the crew shore leave on an uncharted earth-like planet. What
 ought to have been a picnic turns into a nightmare that begins when Dr. McCoy
 see Alice chase the White Rabbit into a hole in the ground, proceeds through
 attacks of a tiger, strafings by a World War 1 fighter, and more, Culminating
 in a knight's lance which kills Dr. McCoy.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Tonia...Emily Banks                     Caretaker...Oliver McGowan
 Rodriguez...Perry Lopez                 Finnegan...Bruce Mars
 Don Juan...James Gruzaf                 Ruth...Shirley Bonne
 Samurai...Sebastian Tom

