@node "Squire_of_Gothos" "Squire of Gothos"

                                 Episode #018
                            @{b}@{i}THE SQUIRE OF GOTHOS @{ub}@{ui}
                               @{fg fill}Paul Schneider@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 01/12/67@{fg text}
                          Director: Don McDougall

  In an allegedly empty region of space, the Enterprise finds a warm starless
 planet with a single inhabitant: Trelane, who dresses like an 18th Century
 dandy and toys with the lives of the Enterprise officers, whom he forces
 down to his planet to attend a banquet.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Trelane...William Campbell              De Salle...Michael Barrier
 Jaeger...Richard Carlyle                Ross...Venita Wolf

