@node "Arena" "Arena"

                                 Episode #019
                                    @{b}@{i}ARENA @{ub}@{ui}
                @{fg fill}Gene L. Coon from a story by Gene Roddenberry@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 01/19/67@{fg text}
                          Director: Joseph Pevney

  An incredibly powerful race abducts Kirk and the Gorn captain of an enemy
 ship--a representative of a race of sentient reptiles--and forces Kirk and
 the Gorn to fight to the death to decide which of their races will be allowed
 to prevail and which will be annihilated. The Gorn is more powerful, but Kirk
 is faster; their intelligences seem matched.

