@node "The_Alternative_Factor" "The Alternative Factor"

                                 Episode #020
                         @{b}@{i}THE ALTERNATIVE FACTOR @{ub}@{ui}
                              @{fg fill}Don Ingalls@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 03/30/67@{fg text}
                           Director: Gerd Oswald

  After a puzzling moment when the starts simply wink out, the Enterprise
 crew discover a single life form on a planet below; his name is Lazarus.
 Soon, it is discovered there are two virtually identical Lazaruses, but
 never are they seen together. One is insane and dangerous, the other
 rational and in pursuit of his mad alter-ego. They are from parallel
 universes, one positive, the other negative; and if the two men should
 ever meet, both universes, ours and the other would be obliterated. 
 Which is what the mad one hopes to do but which one is mad and which
 one is insane?

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

