                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 02/16/67@{fg text}
                          Director: Marc Daniels

  Among those in suspended animation aboard the SS Botany Bay, there's
 Khan, a genetically superior dictator who, in the Eugenics Wars on Earth
 in the 1990's, at one time ruled a quarter of the Earth. Now, reawakened
