@node "City_on_the_Edge_of_Forever" "City on the Edge of Forever"

                                 Episode #028
                         @{b}@{i}CITY ON THE EDGE OF FOREVER @{ub}@{ui}
                               @{fg fill}Harlen Ellison@{fg text}
                         @{fg shine}Original Air Date: 04/06/67@{fg text}
                          Director: Joseph Pevney

  McCoy makes an ill-advised jump through a time portal, ends up in 20th 
 Century America, and does something that alters the course of history. 
 Unless Kirk and Spock can go back and prevent McCoy's blunder, the whole
 history of space exploration, including the construction of the Enterprise,
 will not have occurred. Kirk and Spock go back into the 1930's to a store-
 front mission during the Depression and wait for McCoy to arrive. Meanwhile
 Kirk falls very much in love with the very woman who holds the key to 
 the two possible futures and who must be prevented from meeting McCoy.

